  "keyFeatures": [
    "Zero dependencies — pure Node.js, no external libraries",
    "43 tools across 8 categories: arithmetic, trigonometry, statistics, percentages, unit conversion, constants, memory, and base conversion",
    "Three tool tiers (minimal/standard/full) to optimize AI context token usage",
    "Worker thread isolation with configurable timeout prevents infinite loops",
    "Accurate decimal math via integer-scaling (0.1 + 0.2 === 0.3)",
    "Fuzzy tool name matching with Levenshtein distance correction",
    "80+ unit conversions across 8 categories",
    "16 mathematical, physical, and chemistry constants",
    "LRU result cache (1000 entries, 5-min TTL)",
    "Batch processing up to 50 operations per request"
  ],
